==== Example

Vocabulary size 4.
Model output after softmax for one position: stem:[q = [0.1, 0.6, 0.2, 0.1\]].
Correct token index: 1 (probability stem:[q_1 = 0.6]).

stem:[H = -\ln(0.6) \approx 0.511]

